text: Brooke Irene Austin (born 12 February 1996) is an American tennis player. Austin has a career high WTA singles ranking of 424 achieved on 26 August 2013. She also has a career high WTA doubles ranking of 638 achieved on 27 May 2013. Austin has won one ITF singles title and 2 ITF doubles titles. Austin made her Grand Slam main draw debut at the 2016 US Open in the doubles event, partnering Kourtney Keegan.
